title: EnerWear 10P Pack Unisex Cotton Moisture Wicking Cushion Crew Socks
description: This Enerwear cotton socks are knitted by the most advanced and cutting edge machines, ensuring that every sock is well crafted and comfortable. It’s made of 80% cotton, ensuring that the socks are soft and breathable so that your feet remain comfortable and fresh all day long. They’re 30% thicker and heavier than regular socks and are able to absorb sweat better, making them ideal for sports and athletic activities. Also available in crew and no-show styles.
